no.uib.smo015.info233.oblig2.UIBRoomApp

Class UibRoomApp

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.uib.smo015.info233.oblig2.UIBRoomApp.UibRoomApp

  • public class UibRoomApp
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to represent the application as a whole. The application can fetch activities from a given url, and parse the data back into a list which is easy to look trough. The list is sorted from monday to friday.

    sindremoldeklev
